kpi_info.use: Duration of the measurement period in minutes.

kpi_info.title: IPS_TOTAL

kpi_info.title: SCTP_CURRENT_ESTABLISHMENT
kpi_info.use: The number of associations for which the current state is either ESTABLISHED, SHUTDOWN-RECEIVED or SHUTDOWN-PENDING. UPDATED:When association is established.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_ACTIVE_ESTABLISHMENT
kpi_info.use: The number of times that associations have made a direct transition to the ESTABLISHED state from the COOKIE-ECHOED state: COOKIE-ECHOED -> ESTABLISHED. The upper layer initiated the association attempt. UPDATED:When association is established actively.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_PASSIVE_ESTABLISHMENT
kpi_info.use: The number of times that associations have made a direct transition to the ESTABLISHED state from the CLOSED state: CLOSED -> ESTABLISHED. The remote endpoint initiated the association attempt. UPDATED:When association is established passively.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_RESTARTED
kpi_info.use: The number of restarted SCTP associations due to peer dropped. UPDATED:When association is restarted.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_ABORTED
kpi_info.use: The number of times that associations have made a direct transition to the CLOSED state from any state using the primitive 'ABORT': AnyState --Abort--> CLOSED. Ungraceful termination of the association. UPDATED:When association is closed with ABORT.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_SHUTDOWNS
kpi_info.use: The number of times that associations have made a direct transition to the CLOSED state from either the SHUTDOWN-SENT state or the SHUTDOWN-ACK-SENT state. Graceful termination of the association. UPDATED:When association is closed with SHUTDOWN.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_TOO_MANY_RETRANSMISSIONS
kpi_info.use: The number of associations closed due to excessive retransmissions. UPDATED:When association is closed due to excessive retransmissions.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_RECEIVED_BYTES
kpi_info.use: The number of bytes received in sequence. UPDATED:When an SCTP segment is received in sequence, this counter will be updated to tell how many bytes have been received.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_RECEIVED_PACKETS
kpi_info.use: The number of SCTP packets received. Duplicates and invalid packets are included. UPDATED:When an SCTP packet is received.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_RECEIVED_DATAGRAMS
kpi_info.use: The number of received valid packets. UPDATED:When a valid packet is received.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_RECEIVED_CONTROL
kpi_info.use: The number of SCTP control chunks received (no duplicate chunks included). UPDATED:When an SCTP segment with control chunks is received.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_RECEIVED_OOTB
kpi_info.use: "The number of out of the blue packets received by the host. An out of the blue packet is an SCTP packet correctly formed, including the proper checksum, but for which the receiver was unable to identify an appropriate association. UPDATED:When an SCTP segment is received.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_RECEIVED_DUPLICATED_TSN
kpi_info.use: The number of received duplicated TSN. UPDATED:When an SCTP segment with duplicate TSN is received.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_DROPPED_FRAGMENT
kpi_info.use: The number of dropped invalid fragments. UPDATED:When an invalid fragment is dropped.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_BAD_SSN
kpi_info.use: The number of dropped chunks due to bad stream sequence number. UPDATED:When dropped due to bad stream sequence number.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_BAD_CSUM
kpi_info.use: The number of SCTP packets received with an invalid checksum. UPDATED:When dropped due to bad checksum.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_BAD_VTAG
kpi_info.use: The number of dropped SCTP packets due to bad verification tag. UPDATED:When dropped due to bad verification tag.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_BAD_STREAM_NBR
kpi_info.use: The number of dropped chunks due to bad stream number. UPDATED:When dropped due to bad stream number.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_IN_MULTICAST
kpi_info.use: The number of dropped multicast SCTP packets (SCTP cannot be multicast). UPDATED:When dropped multicast (SCTP cannot be multicast).

kpi_info.title: SCTP_HEADER_DROPS
kpi_info.use: The number of dropped SCTP packets due to bad header. UPDATED:When dropped due to bad header.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_RECEIVE_WINDOW_DROPS
kpi_info.use: The number of dropped SCTP packets due to no receive window. UPDATED:When dropped due to no receive window.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_NO_PORTS
kpi_info.use: The number of dropped SCTP packets due to no endpoint found. UPDATED:When dropped due to no endpoint found.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_NO_MEMORY
kpi_info.use: The number of SCTP chunks dropped due to no memory. UPDATED:When dropped due to no memory.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_SENT_BYTES
kpi_info.use: The number of SCTP bytes sent. UPDATED:When an SCTP segment is sent, this counter will tell how many bytes have been sent.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_SENT_DATAGRAMS
kpi_info.use: The number of SCTP packets sent. Retransmitted DATA chunks are included. UPDATED:When an SCTP segment whose length is more than zero is sent.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_SENT_CONTROL
kpi_info.use: The number of SCTP control chunks sent (retransmissions are not included). Control chunks are those chunks different from DATA. UPDATED:When an SCTP control segment is sent.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_SENT_RETRANSMISSIONS
kpi_info.use: The number of retransmitted SCTP chunks. UPDATED:When retransmitted SCTP data is sent.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_SENT_FAST_RETRANSMISSIONS
kpi_info.use: The number of fast retransmitted SCTP chunks. UPDATED:When fast retransmission is sent.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_SENT_WINDOW_PROBE
kpi_info.use: The number of SCTP chunks sent for window probes. UPDATED:When window probe is sent.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_RECEIVED_CHUNK_DATA
kpi_info.use: The number of SCTP DATA chunks received. UPDATED:When DATA chunk is received.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_SENT_CHUNK_DATA
kpi_info.use: The number of SCTP DATA chunks sent. UPDATED:When DATA chunk is sent.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_RECEIVED_CHUNK_SACK
kpi_info.use: The number of SCTP SACK chunks received. UPDATED:When SACK chunk is received.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_SENT_CHUNK_SACK
kpi_info.use: The number of SCTP SACK chunks sent. UPDATED:When SACK chunk is sent.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_RECEIVED_CHUNK_HBREQ
kpi_info.use: The number of SCTP HEARTBEAT-REQ chunks received. UPDATED:When HEARTBEAT-REQ chunk is received.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_SENT_CHUNK_HBREQ
kpi_info.use: The number of SCTP HEARTBEAT-REQ chunks sent. UPDATED:When HEARTBEAT-REQ chunk is sent.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_RECEIVED_CHUNK_HBACK
kpi_info.use: The number of SCTP HEARTBEAT-ACK chunks received. UPDATED:When HEARTBEAT-ACK chunk is received.

kpi_info.title: SCTP_SENT_CHUNK_HBACK
kpi_info.use: The number of SCTP HEARTBEAT-ACK chunks sent. UPDATED:When HEARTBEAT-ACK chunk is sent.
